textAfterTable: MossRose Albany, MO (Zone 5a) July 2, 2003 10:46 AM Post #571836 Thanks Philomel... MossRose Albany, MO (Zone 5a) July 6, 2003 6:57 PM Post #575588 Here's the germinated seed. Only one has germ'ed so far. By the time I found it the first set of leaves were developing. The photo's aren't that good...I couldn't get a close enough shot and it be clear enough to tell what the heck it was. But I tried. I've set the others outside in the shade for some warmth. It's been so very hot here that my a/c is running 90 to nothing and it gets too cold in here for them to ever be warm. I'll only leave them for a few hours.
